{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_21071.jpg","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"sepiaFrame"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story06","nameNarration":"莉薇娅","narration":"在我搬到公寓里居住之后不久@我从自己的监护人那里收到了信息","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-1"},{"narration":"他说，老师马上就要举行婚礼了@她那么在意我的住址@似乎就是为了给我寄邀请函","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-2"},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":104101,"lipSynch":0,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-3"}],"nameCenter":"莉薇娅","textCenter":"（大概就是那个时候说的@一流的大哥哥吧…）"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104101,"lipSynch":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-4"}],"nameCenter":"莉薇娅","textCenter":"（她当时就经常秀恩爱…）"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104101,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-5"}],"nameCenter":"莉薇娅","textCenter":"…………"},{"chara":[{"id":104101,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-6"}],"nameCenter":"莉薇娅","textCenter":"（我是不是她结婚的阻碍呢）","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":104101,"lipSynch":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-7"}],"nameCenter":"莉薇娅","textCenter":"（可能就是因为我独立了，@她才终于步入了下一个阶段）"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":104101,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-8"}],"nameCenter":"莉薇娅","textCenter":"…………"},{"chara":[{"id":104101,"lipSynch":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-9"}],"nameCenter":"莉薇娅","textCenter":"（如果老师没能结婚@也是因为我的魔法的话）"},{"chara":[{"id":104101,"lipSynch":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-10"}],"nameCenter":"莉薇娅","textCenter":"（我就已经对她造成影响了…）"},{"nameNarration":"莉薇娅","narration":"那时的我其实真的很想去参加婚礼@我心中充满了想见证@照顾过自己的老师幸福的样子的心情","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21071.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-11"},{"bgm":"stop","narration":"所以，我才把事情想得太理想化了","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-12"},{"narration":"因为已经造成了不幸的效果@所以自己去参加也没问题","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-13"},{"narration":"那时的我是这么想的@所以，虽然婚礼本身不会参加@但作为替代，我打算偷偷地见证这一切","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-14"},{"autoTurnLast":2,"bg":"bg_adv_18041.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":104101,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm05_event10","nameNarration":"莉薇娅","narration":"站在教堂旁边，穿着婚纱的老师@真的非常漂亮","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-15"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104101}],"narration":"如果这么幸福的瞬间@是因为我才推迟的话@那么，我真的非常抱歉","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-16"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":104101}],"narration":"而且，已经死去的我的内心@再次能因为他人的幸福而感到喜悦了@对此，我唯有感谢","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-17"},{"narration":"眺望着老师幸福的姿态@我的脑中浮现出了在剧团被杀的同伴们的身影@我觉得，我一定能对大家说出@“我活得真的很好”","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-18"},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":104101,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-19"}],"nameCenter":"莉薇娅","textCenter":"啊…"},{"chara":[{"id":104101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-20"}],"nameCenter":"莉薇娅","textCenter":"老师注意到这边了…"},{"chara":[{"id":104101,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-21"}],"nameCenter":"莉薇娅","textCenter":"等，不能那样跳吧@会踩到裙摆的"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":104101,"lipSynch":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-22"}],"nameCenter":"莉