e/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-44"}],"nameLeft":"莉薇娅","textLeft":"在很久之前@我就亲眼见证过了"},{"chara":[{"id":104101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-45"}],"nameLeft":"莉薇娅","textLeft":"如果就算作为实现愿望的代价@与魔女战斗"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-46"}],"nameLeft":"莉薇娅","textLeft":"最后自己还是会变成魔女的话@人生就真的无可救药了"},{"chara":[{"id":104101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-47"}],"nameLeft":"莉薇娅","textLeft":"而且还无法留下或成就任何东西@只能散布诅咒…"},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-48"}],"nameRight":"丘比","textRight":"才没有那回事"},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-49"}],"nameRight":"丘比","textRight":"你们在变成魔女的时候@会产生巨大的能量"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_042.exp3.json","id":104101,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-50"}],"nameLeft":"莉薇娅","textLeft":"哈？"},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-51"}],"nameRight":"丘比","textRight":"而我们会回收那些能量"},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-52"}],"nameRight":"丘比","textRight":"并将其用于维持宇宙"},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-53"}],"nameRight":"丘比","textRight":"虽说是间接性的，但也可以说@你们确实留下了某些东西吧"},{"chara":[{"id":104101,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-54"}],"nameLeft":"莉薇娅","textLeft":"也就是说，你是为了留存下宇宙@才制造出魔法少女的吗"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":104101,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameNarration":"莉薇娅","narration":"就好像看透了我会变成魔女一样出现的丘比@淡然地说起了留存宇宙的事情","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21421.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-55"},{"narration":"那时，填满我的脑海的@既有「竟敢利用别人的灵魂」这种仇恨的心情@也有如同看见了希望一样明朗的心情","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-4-56"},{"narration":"正是因为发现了@能不再因自己的一举手一投足@让他人变得不幸也能活下去的方法@令人神